divs: Sighting Details I owned a horse ranch in Oregon. (1) This personcame to the ranch, and a very interesting event happened over a period of threedays. Secondly in Calif.a very interesting object appeared every night atapprox. 9:30 with some very interesting routines (all the same) for a period ofweeks. I have never written this down as it is best told in person as to me itis unbelievable. No I was not sucked up or anything so flambouyant, but a veryunusual occurance happened twice! Not to long ago I was watching show on TVabout UFOs and throughout the program I felt like had a lot to contribute inthe way of information to some of the questions they were asking. This info. canonly be given in person. If you are interested I thank you, if not I can keep asecret.
